    dc:date "2021" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Sitana (Squamata: Agamidae) from the Deccan Peninsula Biogeographic Zone of India" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4620912>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4620904>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4620908>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4620910>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4620906> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4620912>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Two uncollected males of Sitana sushili sp. nov. in combat (note the prominent nuchal crest) photographed in Debrigarh Wildlife Sanctuary, Odisha. (Photo: Vivek Sarkar)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4620912/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4620904>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Holotype of Sitana sushili sp. nov. (BNHS 2511) from Sambalpur, Odisha. (A) full body dorsal; (B) full body ventral; (C) dorsal, (D) ventral, and (E) right lateral view of head. Scale bars= 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4620904/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4620908>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Hemipenis of Sitana sushili sp. nov. (CES 13584): (A, C) sulcal view; (B, D) asulcal view. Scale bars= 10 mm. (drawings made by Mohammad Asif)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4620908/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4620910>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. The distribution of Sitana sushili sp. nov. and other species from the Sitana sivalensis complex shown with different symbols. Type localities of each species are marked with a red arrow. Locality numbers correspond to those in Table 1. Note that samples collected from India and labelled here as S. sivalensis are based only on genetic similarity." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4620910/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4620906>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Live image of Sitana sushili sp. nov. (A) Male from near Hirakud dam, Sambalpur, Odisha (Photo: V. Deepak), (B) male in a defensive display from Debrigarh, Hirakud WLS, Sambalpur, Odisha (Photo: Vivek Sarkar). (C) habitat near Hirakud dam, Sambalpur, Odisha (Photo: V. Deepak)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4620906/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

